high_descs: Turn to the right 90 degrees and walk to the table, facing left 90 degrees when you reach it.
Look down at the table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Slice the loaf of bread on the table.
Cross to the other side of the room where the stove and microwave are located.
Open the door on the microwave and place the knife inside.
Walk back to the table on the other side of the room.
Pick up a slice of bread from the table.
Walk back to the microwave on the other side of the room.
Open the microwave door, place the bread inside, close it, cook the bread, open the door, remove the bread, and close the door.
Walk back to the table on the other side of the room.
Place the slice of bread on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of bread that you cooked in the microwave onto the table.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the table in the corner of the room, under the window.
Pick up the knife that is by the spoon off of the table.
Walk closer to the table by moving forward.
Slice half of the loaf of bread on the far right of the table.
Turn to the left and walk to the microwave with knife still in hand.
Open the microwave, place the knife inside, close the microwave.
Turn to the right and walk back to the table.
Pick up a slice of bread from the middle of the loaf.
Turn to the left and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the bread inside, close the microwave, start the microwave, open the microwave, and remove the bread.
Back to, turn to the right and walk back to the table with bread in hand.
Place the bread on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm piece of bread on a table.

high_descs: Turn to the right, go straight then to the left to face the white table in the corner.
Pick up the knife from off of the table.
Continue to face the white table.
Slice the bread on the table.
Turn to the left, go straight, then left, straight to face the microwave above the stove.
Open the microwave, place the knife inside, and close the microwave.
Turn around, go straight then to the right to face the white table.
Pick up a slice of the bread.
Turn to the left, go straight, then left, straight to face the microwave above the stove.
Open the microwave, place the bread inside, wait a second, open the microwave, pick up the bread, and close the microwave.
Turn around, go straight then to the right to face the white table.
Place the slice of bread on top of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place the microwaved slice of bread on the white table.
